      <div class="padding-vertical center mid-text border-bottom">
        About Ninth Valley
      </div>

      <div>
        <p>Ninth Valley was founded during June of 2018 by Alex Heil in Buffalo, New York.</p>
        <p>Ninth Valley is the universal platform for online education linking students to instructors through their courses. Ninth Valley's goal is to make it as easy as possible to learn anything under the stars on your own time.</p>
        <p>We're here to learn. You're here to learn. We're here to teach. You're here to teach.</p>
